r sal de calidad alimentaria el producto cristalino que consiste predominantemente en cloruro de sodio. Se obtiene del mar, de depósitos subterráneos de sal mineral o de salmuera natural."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_9bc1e4d2","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO & WHO. 2012. Standard for Food Grade Salt Codex Standard, No. CXS 150-1985. Rome. https://www.fao.org/fao-who-codexalimentarius","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-04-09T16:38:29"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"en","value":"Food grade salt is a crystalline product consisting predominantly of sodium chloride. It is obtained from the sea, from underground rock salt deposits or from natural brine."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_fe1ab363","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"FAO et OMS. 2012. Norme pour le sel de qualité alimentaire. Norme Codex, No. CXS 150-1985. Rome. https://www.fao.org/fao-who-codexalimentarius","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-04-09T16:39:21"},"dct:modified":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2024-04-09T16:41:43"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"fr","value":"Le sel de qualité alimentaire est un produit cristallin se composant principalement de chlorure de sodium. Il peut provenir de la mer, de gisements souterrains de sel de gemme, ou encore de saumure naturelle."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ar_1299513108989","type":"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#Label","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2002-12-12T00:00:00Z"},"http://rdfs.org/ns/void#inDataset":{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/void.ttl#Agrovoc"},"skos:notation":{"type":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/AgrovocCode","value":"26819"},"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#literalForm":{"lang":"ar","value":"ملح الطعام"}},{"uri":"h